title: Klikkaa mua
overview: Klikkaa mua is a show abou Ella, who has a total of three children with two men. Ella works as an interior designer and showcasing her work on a TV series, her life is so busy she does not have time to get meet new people. So after talking to her friends she decides to create her own online dating profile for the Click Me service and to start meeting men. The series also includes Ellia's kindergarten teacher friend Tiia and Inari, who works as a land surveyor.
